| `shopping.db` | SQLite database file |
| `nginx-config.txt` | Nginx configuration backup |
| `public/index.html` | Homepage and product listing |
| `public/product.html` | Individual product detail page |
| `public/login.html` | User login page |
| `public/register.html` | User registration page |
| `public/admin.html` | Admin panel (protected) |
| `public/change-password.html` | Password change page |
| `public/orders.html` | User order history page |
| `public/js/` | All frontend JavaScript modules |
| `public/css/` | All stylesheets |
| `public/images/` | Product images and thumbnails |

